Rebuild tool
============
Finds all .blend files in the orig/ directory, and convert them
to .dae format, saving the resulting files in the correct directory.

To run the tool, execute this at the command line:
    rebuild.sh

You'll need to have blender installed.


The file export_dae.py is from the Godot Game Engine
http://www.godotengine.org/wp/better-collada-exporter/
It's licensed as GPL v2


Copyright tool
==============
Find 'copyright' files in orig/ and outputh them all into one big file.
This can then be copy-pasted into the debian/copyright file.

To run the tool, execute this at the command line:
    copyright.sh
